{"title":"Kali Invader Open Face Helmet Goes Big, Interceptor v2 Brings all the Features","link":"https://bikerumor.com/kali-invader-brings-full-coverage-w-breezy-open-face-design/","date":1692811553000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1500\" height=\"1092\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-1.jpg\" alt=\"kali OF invader open face trail to enduro mountain bike helmet\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-1.jpg 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-1-297x216.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-1-800x582.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-1-120x87.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-1-768x559.jpg 768w\" /></p>\n<p>Going big but not that big? Or just prefer the added ventilation and easy-drinking style of an open face helmet instead of a full face? The new Kali Invader open face helmet delivers deep coverage without sacrificing great breathability and all of the unique protective features Kali’s known for.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1402\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet.jpg\" alt=\"kali OF invader open face trail to enduro mountain bike helmet shown on riders\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet.jpg 1402w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-297x145.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-800x390.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-120x58.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-768x374.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The OF Invader has their Composite Fusion shell, which uses a thinner shell fused to the EPS foam underneath to create a one-piece structure.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1593\" height=\"1099\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-3.jpg\" alt=\"kali OF invader open face trail to enduro mountain bike helmet\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-3.jpg 1593w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-3-297x205.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-3-800x552.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-3-120x83.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-3-768x530.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-3-1536x1060.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Inside is their RHEON low density cushioning layer that pulls double duty. First, it mitigates low-speed impacts with a softer material, and does so better than standard pads found in most helmets.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Second, it provides non-linear and rotational impact protection because it can squirm and bend, letting the helmet move more than your head and thus potentially decreasing the impact forces that make it to your brain.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1113\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-2.jpg\" alt=\"kali OF invader open face trail to enduro mountain bike helmet\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-2.jpg 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-2-297x220.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-2-800x594.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-2-120x89.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-invader-full-coverage-open-face-enduro-freeride-MTB-helmet-2-768x570.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It comes in matte black only, with an adjustable visor and Fidlock magnetic buckle closure. Two sizes are offered, each with three sets of cheek pads so you can fine tune the fit (and pull them off to wash them).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Claimed weight is 640g and it’s aimed at aggressive trail and big mountain riders, but is not ASTM rated for downhill riding. MSRP is $225 and includes their Lifetime Crash Replacement guarantee.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Kali Interceptor 2.0</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2151\" height=\"1433\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-3.jpg\" alt=\"rider wearing the kali interceptor 2 trail MTB helmet\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-3.jpg 2151w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-3-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-3-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-3-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-3-1536x1023.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-3-2048x1364.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-3-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Coming in a lot lighter at 390g, the Intercepter 2.0 updates one of their best trail mountain bike helmets with RHEON padding, swappable standard and bug mesh padding, gripper panels to hold your sunglasses, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2383\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-2.jpg\" alt=\"kali interceptor 2 trail MTB helmet\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-2.jpg 2383w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-2-297x135.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-2-800x363.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-2-120x54.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-2-768x348.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-2-1536x696.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-2-2048x928.jpg 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Interceptor 2.0 also gets Kali’s Bonehead Nano Fusion tech, which uses dual density EPS foams inside the shell, with cone-shaped patterns that help spread impact forces across a broader area to dissipate them before they reach your head.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1682\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-1.jpg\" alt=\"kali interceptor 2 trail MTB helmet\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-1.jpg 1682w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-1-297x191.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-1-800x514.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-1-120x77.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-1-768x493.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/kali-interceptor-2-trail-MTB-helmet-1-1536x986.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It also gets the Fidlock magnetic buckle and has deep rear coverage, but is open over the ears and has a ton of vents for great air flow. MSRP is $180 and comes in two colors and two sizes, S/M and L/XL.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://kaliprotectives.com\" target=\"_blank\">KaliProtectives.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/kali-invader-brings-full-coverage-w-breezy-open-face-design/\">Kali Invader Open Face Helmet Goes Big, Interceptor v2 Brings all the Features</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"69308ea78a6c5e50c7bed1d1df52d56dba81da19ff34c2c91aae6473508a850d","category":"Cycling"}